# NAME: YouTube_plus
# AUTHOR: steak
# TYPE: Quantumult X Filter
# DESCRIPTION: YouTube / YouTube Music / YouTube Kids / YouTube TV / Googlevideo 全量增强分流规则
# SOURCE: Based on blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script YouTube rules
# UPDATED: 2026-05-11
#
# ================================
# 使用说明
# ================================
# 1. 文件名建议：YouTube_plus.list
# 2. 适用于：Quantumult X [filter_remote]
# 3. 策略组名称：YouTube
# 4. 这是 YouTube 全量增强版，适合 App、网页、电视端、盒子、iPad、YouTube Music、YouTube Kids
# 5. IP-CIDR / IP6-CIDR 已追加 no-resolve，减少不必要 DNS 解析
#
# QX 远程订阅示例：
# https://raw.githubusercontent.com/你的用户名/你的仓库/main/Rules/YouTube_plus.list, tag=YouTube_plus, force-policy=YouTube, update-interval=86400, opt-parser=false, enabled=true
#
# ================================
# 规则来源说明
# ================================
# - 全量域名 / UA / IP：基于 blackmatrix7 Quantumult X YouTube 规则
# - 未加入 HOST-SUFFIX,googleapis.com
# - 未加入 HOST-SUFFIX,googleusercontent.com
# - 未加入 HOST-SUFFIX,gstatic.com
#   避免 Gemini / Google AI / Google 登录 / Google Drive 被 YouTube 策略组误抢
#
# ================================
# 规则统计：全量增强版
# ================================
# HOST: 3
# HOST-KEYWORD: 1
# HOST-SUFFIX: 179
# HOST-WILDCARD: 3
# USER-AGENT: 7
# IP-CIDR: 2
# IP6-CIDR: 1
# TOTAL: 196
#
